p.k: Winner Takes All / The Other Side / The Best Team After months of training for Luchador Day Axel needs Masko to coach him against a pair of uninvited competitors - Madcap and Dynamo! / Axel must 'save' Bobbie Blobby after she defects to Madcap's team tempted by Porcupunk and his assertion that she belongs with the bad toys. / When Madcap and his minions crash a soapbox derby the team must stop the baddies and help Axel - stuck in a car with Luka - cross the finish line!
